price: 26. (Alle) Waa Ogsoonaha Ghaybka (waxaan muuqan ee qarsoon), umana bandhigo Ghaybkiisa qofna.
arabic: عَٰلِمُ ٱلۡغَيۡبِ فَلَا يُظۡهِرُ عَلَىٰ غَيۡبِهِۦٓ أَحَدًا

version.title: Somali translation - Jacob
